  2,147,"The truth (is) from your Lord, so do not be (E) from the doubting/arguing"
  2,148,"And for each a direction/front , he is turning towards it , so race/surpass each other (to) the goodnesses wherever you are, God comes with you altogether , that God (is) on every thing powerful/capable"
