  2,200,"So if you accomplished/carried out your rituals or methods worship , so mention/remember God as you mention/remember your fathers or stronger remembrance, so from the people who say: \"Our Lord, give us in the present world.\" And for him (there is) no share of blessing/fortune in the end (other life)"
  2,201,"And from them who say: \"Our Lord, give us in the present world a goodness , and in the end (other life) a goodness , and protect us/make us avoid the fire`s torture"
